确凿的证据支持我的理论。

183
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:31,860
Horowitz, I beg to differ.
Horowitz，我不同意。

184
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:36,280
Even in your most recent study, the investigative approach was flawed.
即使在你最近的研究中，调查方法也有缺陷。

185
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:40,860
You know as well as I do, the collection of data was not systematic and there's a large
你和我一样清楚，数据收集并不系统，而且存在很大的

186
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:42,020
margin of error.
误差范围。

187
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:45,780
To draw a definitive conclusion based on that data would be misleading.
基于这些数据得出一个确定的结论会误导人。

188
00:07:45,780 --> 00:07:47,660
That is preposterous.
这太荒谬了。

189
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:51,780
You are trying to single-handedly solve one of the world's greatest mysteries, and yet
你试图独自解决世界上最大的谜团之一，然而

190
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:54,180
you're oblivious to the fact that you're wrong.
你却对自己错了这个事实浑然不觉。

191
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:55,900
I am not wrong.
我没有错。

192
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,300
The chicken came first.
鸡先出现。

193
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:59,700
No, the egg came first.
不，蛋先出现。

194
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,700
The chicken.
鸡。

195
00:08:00,700 --> 00:08:01,700
Egg.
蛋。

196
00:08:01,700 --> 00:08:02,700
The chicken.
鸡。

197
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:03,700
The egg.
蛋。

198
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:04,700
The chicken.
鸡。

199
