The egg.
蛋。

203
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:09,700
The egg.
蛋。

204
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,100
So, an interesting question.
所以，一个有趣的问题。

205
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:12,100
