你怎么看？

206
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,020
What came first, the chicken or the egg?
是先有鸡还是先有蛋？

207
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:16,940
Well, you ask me, it was the egg.
嗯，要我说，是先有蛋。

208
00:08:16,940 --> 00:08:17,940
