是先有蛋？

209
00:08:17,940 --> 00:08:18,940
Yeah.
是啊。

210
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:19,940
Interesting.
有意思。

211
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:22,580
What about why did the chicken cross the road?
那为什么鸡要过马路呢？

212
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:23,580
To get to the other side.
为了到对面去。

213
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:25,100
